    <stitle>HOOD, GRILLE, FENDERS AND BUMPER - 7000 - 7000 Model Series - BUMPER</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="1">
        <title>BUMPER</title>
        <para>The 7000 series front bumpers are a stylized one piece steel bumper assembly. The bumper is furnished in
            two styles: the standard bumper (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f0900702">Figure 2, Item 1</hotlnk>) and the swept back style (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f0900702">Figure 2, Item 2</hotlnk>). The swept back bumper is angled at 30 degrees at each
            end.
        </para>
        <figure id="f0900702" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figg09/G0900702.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="352px"
                     scalefitheight="352px"/>
            <caption>Figure 2. Bumper</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1>1. STANDARD FRONT BUMPER</callout1>
                <callout1>2. SWEPT BACK BUMPER</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
    </svcproc>
